import styles from "../styles/Enquiry.module.css"; import ImageUpload from "./ImageUpload"; let name = document.getElementById("customerName"); let email = document.getElementById("customerEmail"); let phoneNum = document.getElementById("customerPhone"); let carMake = document.getElementById("carMake"); let carModel = document.getElementById("carModel"); let carYear = document.getElementById("carYear"); let idle = document.getElementsByName("idle")[0]; let length = document.getElementById("length"); let width = document.getElementById("width"); let height = document.getElementById("height"); function EnquiryForm() { document.addEventListener("submit", function (e) { e.preventDefault(); let formData = { name: name.value, email: email.value, phoneNum: phoneNum.value, carMake: carMake.value, carModel: carModel.value, carYear: carYear.value, idle: idle.checked, dimensions: [length.value, width.value, height.value], }; console.log(formData); }); return (
); } export default EnquiryForm;
